data.name: LocationPermissionText

data.value: Location permission needs to be granted for the application to record your movements.

data.name: MobileDataUsageText
data.value: This will use your mobile connection to upload data. This may result in fees from your mobile operator.

data.name: TransportModeSelectionExplanation

data.name: NoDataInOverview

data.name: SensorPermissionDeniedOpenSettingsiOSText

data.name: SensorPermissionRationaleText
data.value: Motion and Fitness permission needs to be granted for the application to record your movements.

data.name: LocationIntroLabel
data.value: This app needs your location to determine your trips.

data.name: LocationSpecificiOSLabel
data.value: Please select "Always allow" for the app to function.

data.name: MotionIntroLabel
data.value: This app needs your motion data. Your motion data (steps, transportmodes) are used to determine and collect your trips and the locations you visit.

data.name: ThanksText
